This bot will automatically collect from Chumba, Pulsz, Fortunecoins, Luckyland (Stake.us, and Global Poker coming soon).

This bot has been tested and works on windows 11. The libraries used should work on Linux, but would need to be tested.

=============================
| Installation Instructions |
=============================

Automatic install
    - Run the file install-pt1.bat
    - Run the file install-pt2.bat
    
    - Run the bot with run.bat or by "node social.js" in the command line

Manual Install
    - Install node.js / npm (this bot was tested on v19.6.0)
        + https://nodejs.org/en/download
    - Run "npm install" in this directory (without quotes)
    - Edit the config.example.json file to you needs (needs to be saved as config.json)
    - Run the bot with using the run.bat file or by running "node social.js" from the command line in this directory

===========================
| Bot Notes - Please Read |
===========================
- In order to connect to your browser this bot needs to close your existing browser session, and reopen.

- This bot does not sign up, or withdraw from casinos. It only collects the daily login bonuses.

